{
  "abstract": "This chapter reviews the efficacy of biological pesticides (Helicoverpa armigera nuclear polyhedrosis viruses or HaNPVs, fungi, bacteria, protozoa and nematodes) and plant extracts (including Azadirachta indica extracts) against H. armigera; mass production of HaNPVs; and genetic modification of HaNPVs for increased efficacy",
